    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Start-learn-Caffe"><a href="#Start-learn-Caffe" class="headerlink" title="Start learn Caffe"></a>Start learn Caffe</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!apt-get -y install caffe-cuda</span><br><span class="line">!apt-get -y install caffe-cpu</span><br><span class="line">!git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;TimeIsTheChoice&#x2F;caffe.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="no-run-envriroment"><a href="#no-run-envriroment" class="headerlink" title="no run envriroment"></a>no run envriroment</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">!cp &#x2F;content&#x2F;caffe&#x2F;python&#x2F;caffe&#x2F;io.py &#x2F;usr&#x2F;lib&#x2F;python3&#x2F;dist-packages&#x2F;caffe&#x2F;io.py #alter by Yuhang&#39;s rectified code</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="try-to-install-in-windows"><a href="#try-to-install-in-windows" class="headerlink" title="try to install in windows"></a>try to install in windows</h2><h2 id="vast-ai"><a href="#vast-ai" class="headerlink" title="vast.ai"></a>vast.ai</h2>]]></content>
